2)How many types of data stores?
1/Persistent data store,data's durable,
Examples of this are Glacier and RDS.
2/Transient data stores.
The data's just temporarily stored
Examples of this are SQS and SNS.
3/Ephemeral data store.
The data does not stick around,so if you stop the instance
Examples of this are EC2 Instance Store and Memcached data


